# AI Architecture Designer - Environment Configuration
#
# 1. Get a FREE Groq API key at: https://console.groq.com/keys
# 2. Paste it below after the equals sign (no quotes, no spaces)
# 3. Save this file as ".env" (remove ".example" from the filename)
#
# This key is read only by the server-side Python code.
# It is never shown or requested inside the app's interface.

GROQ_API_KEY=your-groq-api-key-here
